    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Search-Score-Send with HITL\n\n**Version:** 2.0 (HITL-enabled)\n**Created:** 2026-03-31\n**Compliance:** GDPR + EU AI Act\n\n### Overview\nAutomated recruitment workflow with **Human-in-the-Loop** approval gates at critical decision points.\n\n### HITL Approval Gates\n\n1. **JD Review** (60 min timeout)\n   - Human reviews extracted requirements\n   - Can edit search queries before execution\n   - Must approve to proceed\n\n2. **Final Review** (24 hr timeout)\n   - Human reviews scored candidates\n   - Reviews generated messages\n   - Can edit messages before approval\n   - EU AI Act compliance: High-risk AI decision\n\n### Input (POST to webhook)\n```json\n{\n  \"jobDescription\": \"string\",\n  \"maxCandidates\": 50,\n  \"scoreThreshold\": 80,\n  \"reviewerEmail\": \"recruiter@company.com\",\n  \"sendMode\": \"queue|immediate\",\n  \"callbackUrl\": \"optional\"\n}\n```\n\n### Real-Time Progress Updates\n- SSE endpoint: `/api/progress/stream/{execution_id}`\n- Updates at: searching, scoring, generating_messages\n- Frontend can show live progress bar\n\n### Compliance Features\n- ✅ GDPR: Zero PII to Claude (anonymization layer)\n- ✅ EU AI Act: Mandatory human review (HITL)\n- ✅ Audit Trail: Complete execution logging\n- ✅ Data Retention: 180 days, then auto-delete\n- ✅ Right to Explanation: Transparent scoring criteria\n\n### Performance\n- Target: < 5 min execution (excl. HITL wait)\n- Parallel search execution\n- Batch API calls for efficiency\n- Real-time progress via SSE",
        "height": 600,
        "width": 380
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-documentation",
      "name": "HITL Workflow Documentation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 600]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "⚠️ **Error Handling**\n\n- All HTTP nodes: 2-3 retry attempts\n- Timeouts configured per node\n- Failed searches don't block workflow\n- HITL timeouts return to requester\n- Progress updates are fire-and-forget",
        "height": 160,
        "width": 280
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-error-handling",
      "name": "Error Handling Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [680, 600]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "🔐 **Security & Privacy**\n\n- Email hashes for deduplication\n- No PII in n8n execution logs\n- Backend anonymizes before Claude\n- HITL approval links expire after use\n- Encrypted database storage",
        "height": 160,
        "width": 280
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-security",
      "name": "Security Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1020, 600]
    }
